title: Grateful Dead Live at Roanoke Civic Center on 1987-07-07
lineage: Master Cassettes were played back with Azimuth adjustment and Dolby decoded on a Nakamichi CD1 into a Korg MR1000 at DSF 1 bit 5.6MHz. Subsequent conversion to 24/96 AIFF done via Korg Audiogate software. Redbook CDR standard 16/44.1 files were created using Bias Peak, Izotope Ozone's MBIT+ (for all dithering), and Weiss Saracon SRC (all sample rate conversions).  FLAC'd using Audiofile Engineering Sample Manager
description:
Set 1

Mississippi Half Step, Walkin' Blues, Candyman, My Brother Esau, When Push Comes To Shove, Me & My Uncle-> Mexicali Blues, Bird Song, Promised Land

Set 2

West L.A. Fadeaway, Cumberland Blues, Looks Like Rain, Eyes Of The World-> Drums-> Space-> The Wheel-> Gimme Some Lovin'-> Morning Dew-> Turn On Your Love Light, E: U.S. Blues
